   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 6 of Lucius Septimius Severus Pius Pertinax Augustus Arabicus Adiabenicus Parthicus maximus, Pauni 23. We, Herminos, son of Valerius, and Neilos, son of Demeas, and partners, sitologoi of the village of Philadelphia, have had measured to us by smoothed public measure [- - -] from the produce of the same 6th year to the credit of Pasipemis, son of Sokopet( ), through Sok[- - -."</ab>
         </div>
